# Knowledge Base Git Ignore Rules

# Hide sensitive logs (keep locally, don't commit)
.kb_logs/

# IDE and editor temp files
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS files
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Backup and temp files
*.bak
*.tmp
*.temp
*.backup
~*

# Do NOT ignore:
# - .kb_config/ (schema and templates should be committed)
# - Actual KB pages (all .md files except templates)
# - README.md and KB_MAINTAINER.md
